fabric.filemanager

Class FabricFileManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • polyglot.filemanager.ExtFileManager
      • fabric.filemanager.FabricFileManager

  • public class FabricFileManager
extends polyglot.filemanager.ExtFileManager
    FileManager implementation for Fabric - a class that provides input and output access to the local file system and input access to the codebase. TODO: store output files in Fabric. Support bytecode sharing between trusted principals
